name: core::num::<impl i64>::strict_abs
doc:
Strict absolute value. Computes `self.abs()`, panicking if
 `self == MIN`.

 # Panics

 ## Overflow behavior

 This function will always panic on overflow, regardless of whether overflow checks are enabled.
